item.description:
To generate the correct payload for each country with ChatGPT:

Create the corresponding JSON files for the following countries AT, CH, DE, PL, CZ including STANDARD, REDUCED, and ZERO Sales Rates. Add the full description of the STANDARD, REDUCED, ZERO Sales Rates. Each country is one JSON file. Use this format:  
{  
"locationCode": "AT",  
"location": {  
"countryCode": "AT"  
},  
"taxClasses": \[  
{  
"code": "STANDARD",  
"name": {  
"en": "Standard"  
},  
"order": 0,  
"rate": 20,  
"isDefault": true,  
"description": {  
"en": "Applies to most goods and services, including food and drink, clothing, furniture, and electronic devices."  
}  
},  
{  
"code": "REDUCED",  
"name": {  
"en": "Reduced"  
},  
"order": 1,  
"rate": 10,  
"description": {  
"en": "Applies to basic foodstuffs, certain medical products and devices, newspapers and periodicals, and certain services."  
}  
},  
{  
"code": "ZERO",  
"name": {  
"en": "Zero"  
},  
"order": 2,  
"rate": 0,  
"description": {  
"en": "Applies to certain goods and services, including most food and drink, books and newspapers, and exports outside the EU."  
}  
}  
\]  
}
